OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1780423900
OL,3,CThe QR keyrings giving 'peace of mind'
OL,4,Cto family of people living with
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,FA Jersey charity hopes a scannable
OL,8,Fkeyring can help people living with
OL,9,Fdementia live safely and independently
OL,10,Ffor longer.
OL,12,FDementia Jersey has adopted MiCode, a
OL,13,FQR code system that people with the
OL,14,Fcondition can carry with them.
OL,16,FThe idea is that if a loved one gets
OL,17,Flost, confused, or is unable to
OL,18,Fcommunicate that they need help, the
OL,19,Fcode can be scanned to access their
OL,20,Femergency contact details and medical
OL,21,Finformation.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1780423900
OL,3,CThe QR keyrings giving 'peace of mind'
OL,4,Cto family of people living with
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,FThe charity now has 500 codes
OL,8,Favailable to Jersey residents, which
OL,9,Fanyone can apply for.
OL,11,FMary's partner, Terry, has dementia,
OL,12,Fand says this will give her peace of
OL,13,Fmind.
OL,15,F"Terry can go out on his own at a
OL,16,Fshort distance, but I worry that I
OL,17,Fdon't know where he is, or he wouldn't
OL,18,Fknow about his medication or phone
OL,19,Fnumbers," Terry explains.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1780423900
OL,3,CThe QR keyrings giving 'peace of mind'
OL,4,Cto family of people living with
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,F"It's very worrying because you don't
OL,8,Fknow where they are, so you hope that
OL,9,Fsomebody realises that he is maybe
OL,10,Flost and brings him back to me, but he
OL,11,Fdoesn't know what to do.
OL,13,F"(The keyring) is very reassuring
OL,14,Fbecause he just says it's (like having
OL,15,Fhis ID) on him. Everything is in one
OL,16,Fplace, so if he gets lost or anything
OL,17,Flike that, I know he's safe."
OL,19,FDr Dawn Harper, a GP and Ambassador
OL,20,Ffor Jersey Dementia Ambassador, has
OL,21,Fbeen supporting the scheme.
OL,26,@uD@BpmuD@NpnvD@[pmwD@Gpn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1780423900
OL,3,CThe QR keyrings giving 'peace of mind'
OL,4,Cto family of people living with
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,F"The patient and the carer can decide
OL,8,Fwhat information goes on there, so it
OL,9,Fdoesn't have to be the entire medical
OL,10,Frecord if there are personal things,"
OL,11,FDr Harper explains.
OL,13,F"It's important things like major
OL,14,Fconditions - dementia being one of
OL,15,Fthem - allergies, medications, and a
OL,16,Fcontract for next of kin."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1780423900
OL,3,CThe QR keyrings giving 'peace of mind'
OL,4,Cto family of people living with
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,FDr Harper says that the developer of
OL,8,Fthe scheme says he heard of one lady
OL,9,Fwith dementia who was picked up by
OL,10,F"well-meaning members of the public or
OL,11,Ffirst responders", but was then taken
OL,12,Fto different emergency departments
OL,13,Fwhere she would have to wait for long
OL,14,Fperiods of time.
OL,16,F"What happens now is her daughter can
OL,17,Fget a telephone call and explain where
OL,18,Fmum lives or find out where she is to
OL,19,Ftake her back.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1780423900
OL,3,CThe QR keyrings giving 'peace of mind'
OL,4,Cto family of people living with
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,F"It's a source of huge reassurance to
OL,8,Fthe daughter, minimises the stress to
OL,9,Fthe lady, and frees up valuable time
OL,10,Fin emergency departments."
OL,12,FDr Harper says that she was inspired
OL,13,Fto get involved with the project as a
OL,14,FGP, with recent experience with a
OL,15,Ffamily member being diagnosed with
OL,16,Fdementia.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1780423900
OL,3,CThe QR keyrings giving 'peace of mind'
OL,4,Cto family of people living with
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,F"My dad is on his own and had a formal
OL,8,Fdiagnosis of dementia at the end of
OL,9,Flast year. I live half an hour away,
OL,10,Fand my brother lives four and a half
OL,11,Fhours away.
OL,13,F"Just knowing that the information
OL,14,Fthat he is starting to get lost, that
OL,15,Fhe has diabetes and high blood
OL,16,Fpressure, is now available on MiCode
OL,17,Fis, for me, peace of mind.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
