OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1780423900
OL,3,CThe QR keyrings giving 'peace of mind'
OL,4,Cto family of people living with
OL,5,Cdementia
OL,7,F"He still goes on holidays (...) say
OL,8,Fif a French person found him and
OL,9,Fscanned the QR code, all the
OL,10,Finformation would automatically
OL,11,Ftranslate into French. It would be the
OL,12,Fsame if he were in Vietnam; it would
OL,13,Ftranslate into Vietnamese (...) I just
OL,14,Fthink this is amazing."
OL,16,FTo get in touch with Dementia Jersey
OL,17,For if you need further support, you
OL,18,Fcan find more details via our Channel
OL,19,FIslands Helplines and Advice.
OL,26,@oD@\pmoD@`pnuD@[pmuD@_pn
